  "Description": {
    "English": "A high thermal energy fuel, contained within a standardized fuel cell. Used to fuel the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Humboldt Drive</span> that powers the Nautilon submarine.<br><br>Created with a mix of organic compounds (<span class=\"name name-fuel\">Carbon</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">cyto-phosphates</span>) and localized mineral <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">salts</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "容纳在标准化燃料电池里的一种高热能燃料。为驱动大鹦鹉螺潜水艇的<span class=\"name name-technology\">洪堡驱动器</span>提供燃料。<br><br>由有机化合物（<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">磷酸细胞</span>）和局部矿物<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>混合而成。",
    "TencentChinese": "容纳在标准化燃料电池里的一种高热能燃料。为驱动大鹦鹉螺潜水艇的<span class=\"name name-technology\">洪堡驱动器</span>提供燃料。<br><br>由有机化合物（<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">磷酸细胞</span>）和局部矿物<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>混合而成。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "含有高度熱能的能量燃料，並以標準燃料電池方式儲存。用以驅動<span class=\"name name-technology\">洪保德驅動器</span>，提供巡洋龍潛艇動力。<br><br>利用混和有機合成物（<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>與<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">細胞磷酸鹽</span>）以及地域性的礦<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">鹽</span>生成。"
  },
